604
00:28:12,020 --> 00:28:15,390
♪ Ang kinalimutang nakaraan ♪

605
00:28:16,370 --> 00:28:18,640
♪ Maaaring may pagsisisi ♪

606
00:28:20,300 --> 00:28:22,540
♪ Maaaring may kalungkutan ♪

607
