subukan ang bilis ng internet sa tanghali.

628
00:29:37,240 --> 00:29:37,870
Okay.

629
00:29:43,120 --> 00:29:47,320
[Purong Hotel]

630
00:29:44,590 --> 00:29:45,240
Umaga.

631
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:47,140
Kumusta, Ms. Xu.

632
00:29:48,390 --> 00:29:50,350
Lahat ay kailangang magsumikap ngayon.

633
00:29:50,350 --> 00:29:51,400
Darating ang mga bisita dito

634
00:29:51,400 --> 00:29:52,860
isa-isa upang mag-check in sa ilang sandali.

635
00:29:52,860 --> 00:29:54,200
Tandaang maingat na suriin

636
00:29:54,200 --> 00:29:55,560
