654
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:48,830
Ito ang presyo ng isang kwarto
sa executive floor pagkatapos ng discount.

655
00:30:48,830 --> 00:30:50,000
Nag-book ka ng executive floor?

656
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:51,470
Ang entrance exam ng aming anak sa kolehiyo ay

657
00:30:51,470 --> 00:30:52,750
