667
00:31:11,790 --> 00:31:13,320
Anong klaseng ama ka?

668
00:31:13,590 --> 00:31:15,520
Sa tingin ko ay hindi na kailangan.

669
00:31:16,100 --> 00:31:17,980
Bakit hindi kailangan?

670
00:31:18,030 --> 00:31:20,610
Sobrang lakas ng hilik mo sa gabi.

671
00:31:20,630 --> 00:31:21,960
Kung hindi ako makakakuha ng suite,

672
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:23,640
