673
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:25,900
Kung ganoon, hindi mo dapat pinayagan ang tatay ko.

674
00:31:25,910 --> 00:31:27,740
Liu Yuze, tumahimik ka na lang.

675
00:31:28,030 --> 00:31:29,240
Sorry sa interrupt.

676
00:31:29,310 --> 00:31:30,410
Paano ito?

677
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:31,830
Mangyaring sundan ako sa executive floor

678
00:31:31,830 --> 00:31:32,950
